headline.print_headline: Nationalists Lead in Race for Bosnia Presidency, Reflecting Divisions
headline.main: Nationalists Lead in Race for Bosnia Presidency, Reflecting Divisions

lead_paragraph: Nationalists with little shared vision of Bosnia's future were in the lead in an election for the three-person presidency on Sunday, likely portending more dysfunction in a country still haunted by the divisions of a 1992-95 war.
